name: Double Dare
overview: Do you DARE? Can you handle the pressure? Do you know the answer? Should you DARE the other team? Can you beat the odds? Do you DARE to take the Physical Challenge? Double Dare is Double Action! Double Dare is Double Fun! Double Dare is the ultimate contest for the whole family! Think fast - test your mind with questions on every subject from Rock to rocks. Move fast - test your skill as those famous DD stunts stretch your reflexes to the limit. You know how it's done, so get out there and rack up the points! But watch out for those obstacles. If you're not careful, you could end up in a real mess!
